text: "I'll Be Fine" is a song by Swedish singer Molly Pettersson Hammar. It was released on 7 February 2015 as a digital download in Sweden.iTunes - Musik - I'll Be Fine - Single av Molly Pettersson Hammar The song was written by Molly Pettersson Hammar, Lisa Desmond, Tim Larsson, Tobias Lundgren and Gavin Jones. The song took part in Melodifestivalen 2015, and was eliminated from the first semi-final on 7 February 2015, placing sixth. The song subsequently peaked at number 65 on the Swedish Singles Chart.
